	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well I finally found a copy of this spell for sale at a reasonable price, so I've got it.&nbsp;&nbsp;The problem is it doesn't proc nearly as often as the Luclin spell (which only draws 25HP's).  I'm still not sure if it procs' enough at 50HP's to offset the higher proc rate of my old spell.<br><br>Reason I'm posting is to warn you guys.  I was offered this spell a month ago for 2k, I reluctantly declined.  Now I'm happy I did, it's definately not worth 2k.  I'm happy with it for 500pp I spent but it's not as great as I expected.  Hopefully you won't run across the same greedy people I have trying to get this spell, but if you do at least you won't feel so bad waiting to get the right price for a less than stellar spell.  Not every rare spell is valuable.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant</td></tr>
